sequenceDiagram
  autonumber
  participant V as Voter browser
  participant A as Admin browser
  participant API as Express API
  participant E as eventBus
  participant DB as Supabase

  V->>API: GET /api/session/stream (Accept: text/event-stream)
  API->>DB: SELECT live_sessions WHERE key='main'
  API-->>V: event: session.snapshot · data: {...}
  API->>E: addClient(res)

  loop heartbeat every 25s
    E-)V: : ping
  end

  A->>API: POST /api/session/votes-visible { visible: true } (Bearer JWT)
  API->>API: protect · adminOnly · zod
  API->>DB: UPSERT live_sessions
  API-)E: broadcast 'session.update'
  E-)V: event: session.update · data: { voteCountVisible: true, ... }
  V->>V: setSession(...) — UI re-renders
